Here are the steps for creating a local variable:

  * Name it.
  * Specify a datatype.
  * If you have specified an Ingres datatype, indicate whether it 
    is nullable.
  * If you have specified a record type, indicate whether it is an array.
  * Enter a short description or comment if you want one.

Refer to the Subtopics for more information.
